Classic:the first year or the first two years of the Business Plan (depending on the number of years chosen) are in Detailed entry  mode. Following years are in Global entry mode.
Global: all years are in Global entry mode. Practical for writing an approximate version of your Business Plan quickly. You may switch to Detailed entry mode at any time without losing your work.
"></i>					</label>

